dialogue.introduction: I'm Satsuki. Good to meet ya!
dialogue.library_intro: I kept getting injured again and again on missions, but I fought bravely to the end as the 5th of the Mutsuki-class destroyers. After the war began, I did my best to escort the fleet and guard areas of the ocean. I really did!
dialogue.secretaryidle: Geez Commander, is it not my turn yet? Are you listening to me? Aah... I see, understood.
dialogue.secretarymarried: Seriously, I'm no match for the Commander... hehe~
dialogue.wedding: Commander! I'm sorry for always making you fret… but… it was a little on purpose… just kidding!
dialogue.equipment1: Looks like you made me stronger. Thanks, Commander!
dialogue.equipment2: Yeah, I'm different from the everyday me!
dialogue.docking_moderate_damage: Woah~ I thought I was really gonna die~
dialogue.ship_construction: Looks like a new friend has arrived.
dialogue.battle_start: You gonna fight with me? Ain't that cute of ya!
dialogue.mvp: Ehehee!! Are you reconsidering me now?
dialogue.sunk: H-hey? What's this... the ocean... is dark... I can't see anything... why?
dialogue.second_anniversary_2015: Today is a special day... Well any day is a special day, as long as you are with me Commander!
dialogue.rainy_season_2015: The season of May...ehe, it's my season, isn't it? Ufufufu!
dialogue.fall_event_2015: This time even I won't go easy on them!
dialogue.christmas_2015: Commander! I heard they're celebrating Christmas in the city. How gallant. What should we do? Just kidding!
dialogue.new_year_2016: Happy New Year, Commander! It's cute how it passed so fast! Take care of me this year as well!
